EverArcade Creator SDK v0.1

Canonical creator workflow:
  everarcade new -> everarcade build -> everarcade test -> everarcade deploy -> everarcade publish

Layout:
  cli/            Creator CLI entrypoint and workflow commands.
  templates/      Opinionated starter projects.
  examples/       Complete game examples that build, deploy, and run locally.
  generators/     Scaffolding helpers consumed by the CLI.
  assets/         Creator asset catalog APIs and example assets.
  inventory/      Items, equipment, containers, and vault asset APIs.
  economy/        Currency, rewards, listings, royalties, and settlement event APIs.
  civilization/   Regions, worlds, settlements, governance, and local economies APIs.
  deployment/     Local, lease, and federation deployment descriptors.
  marketplace/    Creator-facing marketplace publication models.
  monetization/   Non-production monetization models for royalties and rewards.
  onboarding/     First-game workflow guidance.
  success/        Creator success metric definitions.
